{"tid":1632120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海關話你地阻撚住佢收工呀!","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T20:15:47.000Z","uid":222109,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9d1dac055b9abd4ac75844a45f3e68862871c533","tid":1632120,"uid":222109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivDq223.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivDq223.png&h=7bf38085&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n就係你地成日搞事搞到人地洗多一百大元，影響民生!<br />\n究竟海關係咪黑警合作夥伴?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8d36bdaeb2b3e542ea12056c2aafd4b5a9dcc0","tid":1632120,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"41ed479b1f66101b473ba7c42f663ab011d6daaf","tid":1632120,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c899c5f45f115e4d8d4023ddb56a2034c1f952c","tid":1632120,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:50.000Z","msg":"又想開支線？<br />\n辭職未慳番果一百蚊囉"},{"pid":"e430103ea0d4cfe4079670e16afaa05b777bcf69","tid":1632120,"uid":132287,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"咪撚乜都放上連登啦"},{"pid":"7e2b93b318f84e70cd5499c7aa3a1a3f292d3b4a","tid":1632120,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"支那人都可以做公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae085ffc11754200e03c79b0e5fa3e9954bf1b91","tid":1632120,"uid":222109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e2b93b318f84e70cd5499c7aa3a1a3f292d3b4a","tid":1632120,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"支那人都可以做公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:13.000Z","msg":"幾皮野袋袋平安"},{"pid":"e3ac328f923ae3e2958a0fd51c51325e8f60a84b","tid":1632120,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"咪撚乜都放上連登啦"},{"pid":"ebe5af214b9e6b5c15d4190fb6864a7aa09064c2","tid":1632120,"uid":222109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3ac328f923ae3e2958a0fd51c51325e8f60a84b","tid":1632120,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"咪撚乜都放上連登啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"咁討論區乜撚先放得呀"},{"pid":"5fd188b1360f240f6b4606cc8393c977ebfbdbaf","tid":1632120,"uid":248116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e2b93b318f84e70cd5499c7aa3a1a3f292d3b4a","tid":1632120,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"支那人都可以做公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"大把啦<br />\n坐夠七年<br />\n將個支那拼音名換番香港拼音<br />\n你唔睇佢身份證咩字頭<br />\n都唔會知佢地邊度黎"},{"pid":"4662c49a6787084e194903b0cc075c58fabc4a33","tid":1632120,"uid":256330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:15:47.000Z","msg":"口裡愛國身體很誠實"}]}